            <h4>Protein Structure Prediction</h4>
            <img width="400px" align="middle" src="images/actsite_ffx.png" alt="X-ray"/>
            <h4>X-ray Crystallography Refinement</h4>
            <hr/>
            <p>
                Force Field X is a group of open source (GPL v. 3), platform independent modules for molecular biophysics.
                Key algorithms include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Polarizable AMOEBA force fields</li>
                <li>Particle-mesh Ewald electrostatics</li>
                <li>Generalized Kirkwood continuum electrostatics</li>
                <li>X-ray and neutron crystallography refinement</li>
                <li>Real space refinement for CryoEM</li>
                <li>Methods for structure based drug design</li>
            </ul>
            <hr/>
        </section>
